{"tid":2212126,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[潑墨女孩] 董瑤瓊病情加重 不時失禁痴呆、瘋狂尖叫","createTime":"2020-09-21T14:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T13:33:39.000Z","uid":306528,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8fa97298d9f23cccd8746beebfe3681be5d512ed","tid":2212126,"uid":306528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:14:46.000Z","msg":"維權網本月19日透露潑墨女董瑤瓊的最新近況。<br />\n<br />\n董瑤瓊父親指，女兒今年5月被強制關進精神病院近兩個月，她被釋放後病情加重，老是痴呆發傻，反應遲緩，有時候小便失禁都不知要換褲，夜裏有時會瘋狂尖叫，特別是下雨打雷的時候，不讓任何人靠近，令家人十分痛苦。董父亦擔心女兒可能會再被關進精神病院，希望社會關注。<br />\n董瑤瓊今年31歲，本身在上海任房地產公司中介，於2018年7月，她向中共總書記習近平的頭像潑墨後，被上海市警方拘捕；同月16日被上海市警方送回湖南省攸縣鄉下，並以疑有精神病，被關進押於株洲市第三醫院。<br />\n董父指，董瑤瓊拘押期間遭酷刑虐待，被關押在精神病院時曾被強迫吃藥，去年11月獲釋後，活潑開朗的性格變得沉默寡言； 今年5月再被關進株洲三醫院，兩個月後獲釋。<br />\n維權網<br />\n<br />\nSource: Apple daily<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200921/SADENRCOE5AJRHX3GCU6WWLW44/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1ByNUPYHjOVvtKSpXRZ6uRuuKMQl-xUUp03vzm-tbSBU6onfRFJNNhs_M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200921%2FSADENRCOE5AJRHX3GCU6WWLW44%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1ByNUPYHjOVvtKSpXRZ6uRuuKMQl-xUUp03vzm-tbSBU6onfRFJNNhs_M&d=UI3sabJMorhQDzR%2BXF3zEZsm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=d99cd786\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200921%2FSADENRCOE5AJRHX3GCU6WWLW44%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR1ByNUPYHjOVvtKSpXRZ6uRuuKMQl-xUUp03vzm-tbSBU6onfRFJNNhs_M&h=807e4281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200921/SADENRCOE5AJRHX3GCU6WWLW44/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR1ByNUPYHjO